<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>213</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau thiengtho hun sawl inla,
 Lalpa Isu minin;
 Ka lungthim u ah cheng zing hen,
 A nasep mei guolin.

[V2]
 2. Penticost ni a A tunin,
 Suohpihte A panpih;
 A gitlohnau sut banga he'n,
 Mipi chun a ging tau.

[V3]
 3. Khutichun Na na sep theih na'n,
 Thagau thieng ka ngen ui;
 Ei umpih sinsak lungmuon di'n,
 Van ka hung tun mau cheng.

[V4]
 4. Thil dang cheng mu mahleu ung le,
 Zie hih ka taksap uh;
 Gitloh apat ei panpih di'n,
 Thagau maiin A thei.</lyrics>
<title>BANGOR</title>
</song>